query:
INSERT INTO resource (
                id,
                created_date_time,
                modification_date_time,
                resource_name,
                ven_id,
                attributes,
                targets
            )
            VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), now(), now(), $1, $2, $3, $4)
            RETURNING
                id,
                created_date_time,
                modification_date_time,
                resource_name,
                ven_id,
                attributes,
                targets as "targets:Vec<Target>"
